Title: Which Warnings Should I Fix First?
Elements_risk_assessment: A line, l is a bug-related line iff l is modified or removed during any fix-change.
UseOF-SZZ: To locate the fixes and the line bug location
Summary:
They propose a history-based warning prioritization algorithm by mining warning fix experience that is recorded in the
software change history
Outcome:
Their prioritization algorithm improves
warning precision to 17%, 25%, and 67% respectively.
